com.github.jonathanxd.iutils.collection

Interface Walkable<T>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - Type of elements.
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    EmptyWalkable, Walkable.WalkableList

    public interface Walkable<T>
    Walkable is a unification of Collection and Iterator to be used by BiStreams. Walkable is used by BiStream to work with elements.
